<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script type="application/javascript" src="/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/imgs/favicon/favicon.ico">
    <title>Escolher nova senha</title>
</head>

<body class="container bg-light">
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light bg-light mb-4">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
                <img src="/imgs/dashGenLogo.png" alt="" width="60" height="44">
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
                aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/register">Fazer cadastro</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" aria-current="page" href="/login">Entrar</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <%- include('../partials/flash'); -%>

    <h1 class="mb-4">Escolher nova senha</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">Um código de recuperação de senha foi enviado para <%= email %>. Cheque também a
        sua caixa de spam. Caso não tenha recebido o email, tente novamente dentro de alguns minutos.</p>
    <form class="mb-4" action="/changePwd" method="POST">
        <div class="mb-3">
            <label for="email" class="form-label">Código recebido no email</label>
            <input type="text" class="form-control mb-2" id="code" name="code">
            <label for="password" class="form-label">Nova senha</label>
            <input type="password" name="password" id="password" class="form-control" min="5" max="20">
            <input type="email" class="d-none" name="email" value="<%= email %>">
            <% if (typeof message !== "undefined") { %>
            <div class="form-text text-danger"><%= message %></div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Mudar senha</button>
    </form>
</body>

</html>